window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When everyone is sleeping, he comes into their houses.&nbsp;</p> <p>He takes one thing. A photo of their child.&nbsp;</p> <p>A sinister thief on a power trip or something even darker and more sinister?&nbsp;</p> <p>Detectives Jackman and Evans find themselves on the hunt for a highly unusual burglar who seemingly only steals photographs. But then, late one night, an elderly woman falls to her death after seeing someone in her home.&nbsp;</p> <p>Did she really fall, or was she murdered?&nbsp;</p> <p>And just how many mysterious intruders are there on the Fens?&nbsp;</p> <p>With the body count rising, Jackman and Evans have their work cut out for them to track down the night thief - before it’s too late.&nbsp;</p>"; 
